write down a code that will take 3 wfs layers province, Division and districts of Pakistan  uploaded on geoserver through ajax call. there will be three drop down menus on left side. one will ask to select province. unique column of province is "name_1"in province layer. the second drop down will ask to select Division from the selected province. unique column of division is "name_2"  in division layer and uniques column of province in division layer.is "name_1". the third drop down will ask to select districts from divisions . unique column of districts in district layers is "NAME_3" and unique column of division is "NAME_2"  in district layer and unique column of province in district layer.is "NAME_1". once the district is selected right side panel of web app that will be showing that requested district. all of this will be done on an offline leaflet map.there will be reset button to reset all of it .
WFS geojson layer of Province is "http://localhost:8082/geoserver/india/ows?service=WFS&version=1.0.0&request=GetFeature&typeName=india%3Apak_province&maxFeatures=50&outputFormat=application%2Fjson"
 WFS geojson layer of Division is "http://localhost:8082/geoserver/india/ows?service=WFS&version=1.0.0&request=GetFeature&typeName=india%3Apak_state&maxFeatures=50&outputFormat=application%2Fjson"
WFS geojson layer of Division is "http://localhost:8082/geoserver/pk/ows?service=WFS&version=1.0.0&request=GetFeature&typeName=pk%3APAK_adm3&maxFeatures=50&outputFormat=application%2Fjson"
